                     <interp inst="t17800510-55-off303" type="offenceSubcategory" value="burglary"></interp>
               burglariously breaking and entering the dwelling-house of 
                     
                        <persName id="t17800510-55-victim610" type="victimName">
                           Thomas 
                           Gray
                        <interp inst="t17800510-55-victim610" type="surname" value="Gray"></interp>
